    • mbAll

      @Deprecated public static final EditInfoZ mbAll
      Deprecated.
      This selector causes much data to be transfered over the network. Use a combination of EditInfoC.mb values instead, that explicitly define the amount of data to be returned. If only indexing information and document version data is of interest mbSordDocAtt or mbSord should be used. Since 12.00.000.046, this selector will provide EditInfo.mask, EditInfo.sordTypes and EditInfo.keywords for lazy loading.
      All members without mbSmallDocumentContent
